'''Anoat malted''' was a beverage from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Anoat/Legends|Anoat]]. Anoat malted was a rich, sweet beverage known for its deep, smoky flavor. It cost roughly one half-credit, and were sometimes used to dunk [[Gamorrean snack-cracker]]s.

